{"data":{"page":{"id":"9eef36b1-693f-5302-880e-e1f252d9617f","html":"<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/0c187c242ae62c6be8486e9bf4b1bb75/89cd4/1.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 960px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 56.666666666666664%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"1\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/0c187c242ae62c6be8486e9bf4b1bb75/89cd4/1.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/0c187c242ae62c6be8486e9bf4b1bb75/80bba/1.jpg 500w,\n/static/0c187c242ae62c6be8486e9bf4b1bb75/89cd4/1.jpg 960w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<p>At some point, while working in Webmarket, I was contacted by Leonardo Olazabal, the founder of the Shambala Roerich museum in Bedia, Bizkaia.</p>\n<p>He needed help with the maintenance of the museum’s website, which at that point, was using Joomla. I helped him with a few changes and we decided to build a new template with more features, like video player, better blogs taxonomy, etc:</p>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/b57206e73f9eaf49cda644d44266deda/877ff/2.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 1000px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 63.3%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"2\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/b57206e73f9eaf49cda644d44266deda/877ff/2.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/b57206e73f9eaf49cda644d44266deda/d2504/2.jpg 500w,\n/static/b57206e73f9eaf49cda644d44266deda/877ff/2.jpg 1000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<p>A year later, we decided to build a responsive website using Wordpress and implement an e-commerce module to sell his books.</p>\n<p>I am also very grateful to Leonardo and his wife Petri for having supported my <a href=\"http://joanmira.com/samurairoute\">Samurai Route</a> trip with their sponsorship.</p>","fields":{"prefix":"16 December 2009"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Shambala Roerich","cover":null}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/shambala-roerich/","source":"work"}}